						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Marscaleb wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Field =/= frame.</div><br />Progressive =/= interlaced.<br /><br />What do you find confusing about this? Are you just used to modern LCD TVs that only implement 480i, and incorrectly interlace a 240p signal like the NES into 30 hz frames?</div>

