					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The use of fixed-point (fractional) math for subpixel position and velocity in videogames is a well-documented thing, producing the results you see. It's more or less required for reasonable handling.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
