				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p164842">Re: NES and framerate</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=164842&amp;sid=052752976cf1e353c61c9ee952854b07#p164842"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Feb 20, 2016 6:37 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
